    <item>
      <title>拜登计划表达对新日铁交易的担忧，美国钢铁下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/us-steel-falls-on-report-biden-will-voice-concern-on-nippon-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，总统乔·拜登预计很快将发布一份声明，对新日铁公司收购美国钢铁公司的提议表示担忧。这家总部位于匹兹堡的公司的股价创下近四年来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/us-steel-falls-on-report-biden-will-voice-concern-on-nippon-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 16:54:40 GMT</pubDate>
